#aboutModal.modal.fade{"aria-hidden": "true", "aria-labelledby": "aboutModalLabel", role: "dialog", tabindex: "-1"}
  .modal-dialog{role: "document"}
    .modal-content
      .modal-header
        %h5#aboutModalLabel.modal-title About Courier Bot
        %button.close{"aria-label": "Close", "data-dismiss": "modal", type: "button"}
          %span{"aria-hidden": "true"} Ã—
      .modal-body
        %p= "My name's Etienne, I built Courier Bot as a SMS reporting proof-of-concept. This application is the result of observations I made by reading about projects used in humanitarian aid and disaster relief over the past years (projects such as #{ link_to 'FrontlineSMS', 'https://www.frontlinesms.com/', target: '_blank'}, #{ link_to 'Ushahidi', 'https://www.ushahidi.com/', target: '_blank'}, #{ link_to 'Needslist', 'https://needslist.co/', target: '_blank'}...).".html_safe

        %p Courier Bot is for demo-purpose only. To get to a production-ready state would require validation from people who have experience in the fields I mentioned above.

        %p= "From a technological point of view, this project was built using Rails 5. I had an opportunity to explore the #{ link_to 'TwilioSMS', 'https://www.twilio.com/', target: '_blank'} API and functionalities and the use of Websockets through Rails 5 #{ link_to 'ActionCable', 'https://guides.rubyonrails.org/action_cable_overview.html', target: '_blank'}. This project also uses Devise for authentication, Bootstrap 4, and Redis.".html_safe

        %p= "If you have any questions or feedback, please feel free to send me an email at #{ link_to 'mail@etiennebaque.com', 'mailto:mail@etiennebaque.com' }.".html_safe

        %p= "Thanks for giving Courier Bot a try! :-)"
      .modal-footer
        %button.btn.btn-primary{"data-dismiss": "modal", type: "button"} Close
